name: BBChickens
description:
#BBCs are a burnable NFT backed by staked Beets (80/20 Beets/FTM). BBCs are the most liquid NFT on FTM, this liquidity will be achieved by rewarding the burning of our NFT.

90% of the mint proceeds goes to the dao treasury
4.5% of each secondary sale goes to the dao treasury
8.5% of each BURN goes to the dao treasury
